# Backrooms UI

See `docs/UI.md` for full palette.

- Wallpaper: mustard yellow `#D4B84A` / `#E8D174`
- Carpet: beige `#B8A88A`
- Ceiling: off-white panels `#E8E4D9`
- Labels: dark brown `#3D3428`

## Policy

- Original seamless tiles only in `assets/ui/`
- `BackroomsLookAndFeel` for knobs; `WallpaperComponent` for background
- No fluorescent flicker animation in v0.1.x (static UI)
